    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Glassware produced when hot molten glass is poured into a mold and made to conform to it by means of a plunger; the interior form is independent of the exterior form.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
